# vue-vben-admin template files - DO NOT commit these to repository
# Team should pull template from https://github.com/vbenjs/vue-vben-admin
# 
# Whitelist strategy: Only apps/ and 项目部署指南.md are committed
# All other files are from the template and should be ignored

# Ignore everything in vue-vben-admin
vue-vben-admin/*
vue-vben-admin/*/

# But NOT these directories and files
!vue-vben-admin/apps/
!vue-vben-admin/apps/**/*
!vue-vben-admin/项目部署指南.md
